{
  "stem": "19895.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and there were many religious people who-- who were indeed praying more than I did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I did my prayers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was never publicly showing it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just murmured it to myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever I remembered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever I remembered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you say, I negotiated with father, over here, nobody checked on me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember that the more I was praying according father's wish, that's better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and then came the time when-- when they evacuated the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Suddenly, when we heard these murmurs from the distance, the commanders, the SS-- there was an SS commander who-- who we nicknamed Z, the black horseman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We remembered some American movies years back as children, or some older ones, who remembered some Z, the black horseman in some American movies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this guy was an SS commander.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we remember-- I remember German commanders there, the Tudt, T-U-D-T, Tudt organization, who were the architects of the German military.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a commander of that unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the Wehrmacht, which is the German army, was present there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then a bunch of SS people who were under the commander, who were then commanding the Arrow Cross people and the [NON-ENGLISH], the Austrian people who volunteered to work in the camps.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were not uniformed in the same fashion as the Germans or the Arrow Cross people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they were uniformed by armbands of the Volksbund and civilian organizations who were soaked and inundated by Nazi ideas and they volunteered to do the dirty work for them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when that situation was going on, the-- the Russians were approaching.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They lined us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they said that the camp will be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
